::Zardus/Reptilica/Bloodystrike/Perndabot::

An evil smile creeps across Zardus' face as he sees Iron Raptor and Tavatron 
aproach his hiding place. This was sure to prove ... interesting. With a 
silent command from Zardus, the four jump out of the bushes, guns ready and 
surrounding the maximals.

"How nice to see you, maximals," Zardus says, smiling evilly at the 
surrounded maximals. It would be very stupid of them to fight at this point, 
they were outnumbered two-to-one, "You are going to accompany us back to my 
base. Resistance will result in your deaths."

Reptilica and Bloodystrike, standing behind Iron Raptor and Tavatron, raise 
their weapons, aiming them at the maximals' necks. Perndabot stands by 
Zardus' side, dwarfing all the other bots with his giant size, his rifle 
aimed at Iron Raptor's head.
